sourced locally, but the spices,

03:20.501 --> 03:22.534
We actually source them from
local farmers in nigeria.

03:24.371 --> 03:25.503
So you bring the peppers in
yourself from africa?

03:25.572 --> 03:26.804
Yes, yes.

03:26.874 --> 03:28.974
