04:17.324 --> 04:19.491
That's great.

04:19.559 --> 04:21.226
So the last 12 months, how much
revenue have you done?

04:22.696 --> 04:25.363
So we've done about $60,000,
and we're projecting to do

04:25.432 --> 04:26.898
